title: Neo-Nazi Leader Thomas Sewell Heckled Outside Court Over Camp Sovereignty Attack | 10 News
description: Neo-Nazi leader Thomas Sewell has faced off with an angry stranger, who felt compelled to call the "White Australia" fighter "a racist" as he left court.
